and how the small\ncorrections due to the presence of the radial electric field and the vertical\npitching motion of themuons (betatron motion) in the storage ring are taken\ninto account.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 May 2018 21:45:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Jun 2018 21:08:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-03"}
