 S4 with multiple adjacent second-row atoms. The average absolute\ncore-core/core-valence ratio is 0.08 for the first-row species in W4-17, but\n0.47 for the second-row subset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 May 2018 05:15:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-15"}
