nemerges for groups which predict purely imaginary $p$. We present detailed\npredictions of the allowed ranges of neutrino mixing angles, phases and the\nlightest neutrino mass for three of the lowest $\\Delta(6 n^2)$ groups with\n$n=2,4,6$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 May 2018 05:23:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 24 Jul 2018 02:58:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
