autionary note is provided about\nparallax-dependent LPV attributes published in the catalogue. This first Gaia\ncatalogue of LPVs approximately doubles the number of known LPVs with\namplitudes larger than 0.2 mag, despite the conservative candidate selection\ncriteria that prioritise low contamination over high completeness, and despite\nthe limited DR2 time coverage compared to the long periods characteristic of\nLPVs. It also contains a small set of YSO candidates, which offers the\nserendipitous opportunity to study these objects at an early stage of the Gaia\ndata releases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 May 2018 10:20:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 13:22:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
